Global Tungstic Acid Market Insights
Tungstic Acid Market size was valued at USD 0.45 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.73 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Tungstic Acid Market Overview
The Tungstic Acid Market has witnessed significant growth in recent years, primarily driven by the increasing demand for tungsten products in various industries. The global market for Tungstic Acid was valued at approximately USD 500 million in 2024 and is expected to expand at a steady CAGR of 5% from 2025 to 2030. As a key precursor in the production of tungsten chemicals, Tungstic Acid plays a critical role in sectors such as electronics, aerospace, and chemicals. The market dynamics are influenced by industrialization, technological advancements, and the growing utilization of tungsten in renewable energy applications.

